{
  "stem": "5259.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "And in no man's land, the Germans were shooting on random.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "Just shooting in the air.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "Shooting.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 87,
      "text": "And I wore a little coat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 88,
      "text": "And through this coat went out a bullet, went through a bullet.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 89,
      "text": "It didn't touch me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 90,
      "text": "It's a shame that I don't have this coat with me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 91,
      "text": "But it was a coat with a hole in it from a bullet.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 92,
      "text": "We finally crossed the border and came to Russia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 93,
      "text": "We came to [SIGHS] to a town by the name of Lodz-- sorry-- Luck.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 94,
      "text": "And in this town, my father either-- I don't know how it happened.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 95,
      "text": "We lived in with a Jewish family, with very, very poor family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 96,
      "text": "And I was playing with this little boy, living in a place without a window.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 97,
      "text": "And I was just playing with this boy, because I was small, and he was probably my age or a little bit older.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 98,
      "text": "And my parents, of course, had to go and earn a living.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 99,
      "text": "We were there for a short time, a few months, I think.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 100,
      "text": "That the Russians, one night, they came.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 101,
      "text": "And they put us into cattle wagons, and we went.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 102,
      "text": "For three weeks, we were in this cattle wagon and went to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 103,
      "text": "We came to Siberia, to a camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 104,
      "text": "And in this camp-- I don't know-- we stayed very, very short time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 105,
      "text": "But my-- I remember that when we came to this camp, to those barracks, the barracks were still like warm from people who were before.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 106,
      "text": "And apparently, those people were the Germans that they were before there, because they were also concentrated there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 107,
      "text": "And we came in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 108,
      "text": "It was a very remote place in Siberia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 109,
      "text": "It's called taiga.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 110,
      "text": "And we stayed there for a short time.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
